        A construtor creating a gateway with a given xPos, yPos, environment and transmission power.
        Parameters:
        gatewayEUI - gateway identifier.
        xPos - The x-coordinate of the gateway on the map.
        yPos - The y-coordinate of the gateway on the map.
        environment - The map of the environment.
        transmissionPower - The transmission power of the gateway.
        Effect:
        creates a gateway with a given name, xPos, yPos, environment and transmission power.
